      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in stunning, like-new condition inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh feel you'd expect from a showroom floor. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
