    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This example features the 13B-REW power plant with its sophisticated sequential twin-turbocharger system, providing seamless boost transition and a high-revving power band. The chassis retains its ideal 50:50 weight distribution, supported by a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for precise turn-in and lateral grip. Meticulously maintained, the vacuum system is fully pressurized, and the five-speed manual transmission offers short-throw engagement with no synchro wear. This unit is free of structural oxidation and retains its original interior ergonomics, representing a rare opportunity to own a pure, unmolested analog icon in concours-ready condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
