    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in breathtaking, showroom-ready condition. Finished in its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, the exterior is entirely free of chips, swirls, or imperfections, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery retains its factory-fresh scent and shows zero signs of bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity audio system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous, fully documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. There are absolutely no leaks, no rattles, and the engine delivers smooth, effortless power. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, smells, and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
